properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 20 at 3:06AM MST until February 20 at 8:00PM MST by NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds 25 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Portions of El Paso and Dona Ana Counties immediately
west of the Franklin and Organ Mountains. This includes the I-10
corridor between the west side of El Paso and Las Cruces.

* WHEN...From 7 AM this morning to 8 PM MST this evening.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...A strong backdoor cold front will bring
strong easterly winds to the region beginning later this
morning. Cross winds will develop along Interstate 10 between
west El Paso and Las Cruces.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM THIS MORNING TO 8 PM MST THIS EVENING
